satellite.heading: Satelit
satellite.specs:
Ukuran: 50 x 58 x 64 mm
1P PocketQube
Bobot: 245 gr
Bahan: aluminium, emas, fiberglass, lan komponen elektronik.
Orbit: Altitude 525 ± 25 km; inclination: SSO 97,6 ± 0,1 °
Launcher: PSLV (Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle) dilakokno dening ISRO

antenna.heading: Antena / Patung
antenna.specs:
Ukuran: 6 m (diameter) e 1,2 m (dhuwur)
Bobot: 46 kg
Bahan: aluminium, papan pangilon epoksi, kubah aluminium emas sing digantung liwat struktur scaffolding.
